Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:41.00,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(500,500)}本字幕由豌豆字幕組&風之聖殿字幕組聯合製作 \N僅供學習交流 禁止用於商業用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.00,zhu,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:09.23,oped,,0,0,0,,風兒也好 鳥兒也罷 都不及我自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:16.28,oped,,0,0,0,,沒有翅膀就飛奔吧 不論什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:19.08,oped,,0,0,0,,心之所向 無所不及
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:34.76,oped,,0,0,0,,總是出乎想像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:41.35,oped,,0,0,0,,雖然無法做到完美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.15,oped,,0,0,0,,但我心底有一泓清泉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:50.07,oped,,0,0,0,,無論多麼消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:54.36,oped,,0,0,0,,都能讓透明之物充滿內心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:01:01.04,oped,,0,0,0,,這到底是 怎樣一種 奇妙的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:06.88,oped,,0,0,0,,讓我狂熱 讓我痛苦 讓我發笑 以致流下眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:12.67,oped,,0,0,0,,風兒也好 鳥兒也罷 都不及我自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:19.35,oped,,0,0,0,,沒有翅膀就飛奔吧 不論什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:21.60,oped,,0,0,0,,心之所向 無所不及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.02,oped,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:54.93,oped,,0,0,0,,那天的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:58.65,oped,,0,0,0,,我仍銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:04.40,oped,,0,0,0,,希望 色彩 戀愛和夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:08.28,oped,,0,0,0,,{\pos(647,717)}永不放棄的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:17.91,oped,,0,0,0,,我們雖已長大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:29.55,oped,,0,0,0,,那寶物卻永恆不變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:32.55,oped,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644.8,717)}沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:39.73,oped,,0,0,0,,信念就是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:46.23,oped,,0,0,0,,就算現在略有羞澀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:50.86,oped,,0,0,0,,卻也心照不宣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.03,0:23:51.95,oped,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:57.70,oped,,0,0,0,,在我們心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:01.96,oped,,0,0,0,,有一顆閃閃發光的 jewelry
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.96,0:24:05.59,oped,,0,0,0,,隨時隨地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:09.59,oped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,521)}都在賦予我勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:11.64,oped,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早安 秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早安 海渡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早餐的雞蛋 你想吃什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天想吃西式炒蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}軟軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}軟軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}睡得還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 我又做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}又做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我站在高處 看著一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還是不知道那個人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 我有個很想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在看著有那個東西的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}昨晚的夢裡我知道了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:02:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你之前說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不知道為什麼會看著那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 但是今天我知道原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還說了「我想要你手中的東西」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}夢境應該也在慢慢發展吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}發展？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是我什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是你的意識在發展
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在這次的夢裡 你不是知道你在那裡的原因了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那我是不是也能知道我看著的人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:53.63,biaoti,,0,0,0,,小櫻和冰凍的球類大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為什麼不叫醒我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也才剛醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我明明定了鬧鐘的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你把鬧鐘關掉了 邊哼哼邊關掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那你不是醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不 那是半睡半醒的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我還想多睡一會的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}肉包子還剩了一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是又睡著之後就變成棒球比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雪兔哥給我的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}筆袋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}手帕和毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}體操服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還不是多虧了我的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 早飯做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早安 小櫻 你睡過頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早安 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你不是說今天也回不來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 不過家裡有要確認的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還想看看你和桃矢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}把果汁從冰箱裡拿出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他早上要打工 不過是吃過飯才走的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也早點起來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好想和爸爸多待一會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抱歉 最近總是不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事 畢竟工作要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且你也很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 發現好東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊 感覺還會發掘出更多珍貴的東西 一直很激動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我會為你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝 我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了 你說想給朋友看地下的書吧 是哪個朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 她叫秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}桃矢稍微收拾了一下 隨時都可以進去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:06:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要是她來的時候我在家就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好想給你介紹 她人很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}交到了好朋友真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊 秋穗今天也會在學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}上學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}上了國中也還是沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.31,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\frz286.5\pos(242,260)\fad(482,0)}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}經常會覺得她還是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也經常會覺得她已經長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 她確實是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今後也請一直守護她 撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}虧你還說要遲到了 結果早飯還是吃了那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好久沒和爸爸一起吃早飯了 而且也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真好啊 吃了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小肉餅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好想吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼嘛 原來是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早安 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好少見啊 這個點居然還能碰到你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊 準備出門的時候 偉剛好打電話過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}聊久了點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}偉先生還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}畢竟我是一個人住 他很擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}畢竟以前一直住在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他很擔心還很幼稚的小鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們快點走吧 不然真的要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}安全到校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}同學們早安 回到座位上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好久沒見你踩點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}急死我了 不知道小狼趕上了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們一起來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早間約會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不 小櫻睡過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那麼 今天從第三節課開始是球類大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家齊心協力好好享受吧 小心不要受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}千春是打排球對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對 柚子你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}籃球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真是激動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我期待你的活躍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}希望天氣能一直晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}天氣預報說今天是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:08:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在球類大賽上 學生是不能攝影的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你很想拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不是還有我在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真不愧是小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我就知道會有這種事 就帶了備用攝影機 知世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還想拍點小櫻以外的人讓影片更有激情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是知世應該不需要別人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}1年2班獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們超級帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們那邊怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}贏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}很棒的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家都很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗的對手是李同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}兩人都好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}李同學很擅長運動 這是我以前就知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒想到秋穗也這麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}她之前說過她喜歡網球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但沒想到羽毛球打得也很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}居然能讓那個小鬼撿球 她挺厲害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個要打到多少分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}先拿到21分的獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我想同時給他們兩個加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}果然還是希望小狼和秋穗都能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}能不能平手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家到裡面去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}快回教學樓裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們也到裡面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}快點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}老師說先等冰雹停下來再說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼 你組織委員的工作沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我交給山崎了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且 現在這邊更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}果然 這場冰雹只以友枝中學為中心在下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}老師們也很困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}卡牌幹的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要是這樣的話 小櫻 這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我早就料到會有這種事 就準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}防水性能一級棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不管是服裝還是攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你真是太厲害了 知世
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}只是 在這種冰雹當中不能用無人機拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那麼 就讓我用這翅膀和機動力來代替它拍攝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「反射」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}學校被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「反射」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}只是反彈回去的話 學校會被破壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有什麼方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下得越來越多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}冰雹就是冰 要對抗它的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就用熱的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:14:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒 沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有火焰系的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}上啊 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}火神招來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}看來這種程度的法術不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:15:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}無主之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以夢之杖 為吾之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}固著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「HAIL」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 你沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有 知世你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 知世 李同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}冰雹下得太厲害了 我以為你們躲在哪個地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家都在找你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抱歉 讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 你的這身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這 這是 那個 秋穗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這 這是 那什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真漂亮啊 又是舞台劇要用的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下次會是怎樣的舞台劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了 之前你跟我說的那個演公主的舞台劇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也請一定給我看看錄影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}給她看不就行了 那個舞台劇的錄影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}明明很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說起來 很糟糕吧 冰雹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雪兔哥那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一直是晴天哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對不起 什麼忙也沒幫上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你能像這樣和我聊天 就是很大的幫助了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了 桃矢回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒 他發簡訊說要晚一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他在代替感冒請假的人幹活 所以要晚一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然總是跟他說不要勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雪兔哥也狠狠地說他幾句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}狠狠地？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}哥哥太高估自己的身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}明明發起燒來就很難退下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我知道了 我會狠狠說他的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 你跟他說應該會更有效
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他根本不聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}哥哥就知道使壞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:15.81,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}前幾天居然還真的做了蒟蒻飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}關於講故事的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對方說很歡迎你來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你今天很累了吧 好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雪兔哥也是 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}晚安 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真少見啊 連晚飯也沒吃 回來就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他最近真的睡得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也睡吧 雖然還早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}晚安 小可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}又是這個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}鐘錶的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你還是想要鑰匙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也不知道為什麼會在夢中得到這個鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:21:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.27,0:24:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:13.01,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}交給小可
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家有好好運動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.69,0:24:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}又到了文武雙全的「交給小可」環節
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.82,0:24:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這次介紹的仍然是戰鬥服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:21.39,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也給我做一套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.61,0:24:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}易穿脫的披風樣式的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.28,0:24:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}即使是球類大賽中的意外 也能夠順利應對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.09,0:24:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}肩膀上有翅膀 很適合小櫻 感覺不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.13,0:24:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗羽毛球打得也太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.14,0:24:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我看比賽看得太入迷了 沒有怎麼拍到小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.56,0:24:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不要告訴知世哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.42,0:24:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.76,0:24:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}苺玲從香港回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.85,0:24:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}她突然出現嚇了我一跳 真是太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.12,0:24:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且 她還要住我家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.34,0:24:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下集 小櫻和剛回來的苺玲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.11,0:24:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和小櫻一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.52,0:24:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.92,0:24:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}
